about.summary: DeepSMILES - A variant of SMILES for use in machine-learning

name: deepsmiles
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "deepsmiles" %}
{% set version = "1.0.1" %}

package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://github.com/nextmovesoftware/{{ name }}/archive/{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 013dda57525799f8c63c05c2e920bf3fcab70d47af2f4d175846bf1a3799eb56

build:
  noarch: python
  number: 0
  script: "{{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv"

requirements:
  host:
    - python
    - pip
  run:
    - python

test:
  imports:
    - deepsmiles

about:
  home: https://github.com/nextmovesoftware/deepsmiles
  license: MIT
  license_family: MIT
  license_file: LICENSE.txt
  summary: 'DeepSMILES - A variant of SMILES for use in machine-learning'
  dev_url: https://github.com/nextmovesoftware/deepsmiles

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - simonbray
